<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333; } h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom:
      20px; } h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px; } p { margin-bottom: 15px; } .otp { font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 5px; text-align: center; margin-top:
      10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    <p>You recently requested to reset your password. To complete the process,
      please use the following one-time password (OTP):</p>
    <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
    <p>Enter the OTP on the password reset page to set a new password for your
      account.</p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you,<br />
      The Team</p>
  </body>
</html>